fields.name: TBA Note
fields.value: *$1MM not available with Cash Benefit Rider

fields.name: Optional Riders Header
fields.value: OPTIONAL RIDERS AVAILABLE WITH BOTH SIMPLE ADVANTAGE AND CUSTOM ADVANTAGE

fields.name: Shared Care Rider
fields.value: Insured and spouse/partner can access benefits under each other's policy once the TBA under their own policy is exhausted; when insured dies, remaining TBA under his/her policy is transferred to the spouse's/partner's policy at no extra cost; rider available at any time, subject to underwriting; both spouse/partners must have identical policies

fields.name: Nonforfeiture Rider
fields.value: Provides some benefits if policy lapses for nonpayment of premiums or is cancelled by insured; rider must be in effect for 3 years and be in effect when the policy ends; provides full MBA and a reduced TBA equal to the greater of: the total amount of premium paid; or 1x MBA; available at initial application only

fields.name: Cash Benefit Rider
fields.value: Full MBA paid as cash payment (regardless of actual charges incurred) instead of reimbursement for covered services; available at initial application only; $1MM TBA not available; benefits paid over annual IRC limit may be taxable

fields.name: Guaranteed Purchase Option (GPO) Header
fields.value: GUARANTEED PURCHASE OPTION (GPO) (INCLUDED WITH SIMPLE ADVANTAGE ONLY)

fields.name: Guaranteed Purchase Option (GPO) Details
fields.value: Insured able to purchase additional coverage every 3 years, up to age 65, with no additional underwriting; premium for increase in coverage is at attained age rates; lifetime maximum increase available is 2x initial TBA and 2x initial MBA; minimum of 25% of initial coverage must be purchased each time GPO is exercised; increases will not occur if insured is eligible for benefits; if insured rejects two increase offers in a row rider will end; rider ends at the earlier of: policy anniversary date after insured's 65th birthday or when the insured is no longer eligible to receive offers under this rider; insured's premium will be reduced at any time that this rider ends; 10 Year Premium Payment Rider is not available with GPO

fields.name: Benefit Increase Options Header
fields.value: BENEFIT INCREASE OPTIONS (AVAILABLE WITH CUSTOM ADVANTAGE ONLY)

fields.name: Future Purchase Option (FPO) / Benefit Increase Details
fields.value: Increases the MBA and remaining portion of the TBA automatically by 5% of the MBA/remaining TBA in effect at the end of the previous policy year; increases occur unless insured rejects, in writing, prior to the Policy Anniversary of the year in which the increase is to take effect; corresponding increase in premium for increase in coverage at attained age rates; if insured rejects two times in a row, insured will no longer receive automatic increases but can request to have offers reinstated with no additional underwriting; increases will not occur if insured is eligible for benefits; rider available at any time, subject to underwriting; 10 Year Premium Payment Rider is not available with FPO

fields.name: Automatic Compound Inflation Protection Riders
fields.value: Increases the MBA and remaining portion of TBA in effect at the end of the previous policy year, either 3% or 5%, with no corresponding increase in premium; coverage increases continue while insured is eligible for benefits; rider available at any time, with additional underwriting; 3% Automatic Compound Inflation Protection Rider; 5% Automatic Compound Inflation Protection Rider

fields.name: Footer Disclaimer
fields.value: FOR PRODUCER OR BROKER/DEALER USE ONLY. NOT FOR PUBLIC DISTRIBUTION.

fields.name: Footer Company Name
fields.value: Metropolitan Life Insurance Company (MetLife)
